{"tid":953680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人郭紹傑昨起在日本拘留所絕食絕水抗議","createTime":"2018-12-24T06:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T11:31:26.000Z","uid":41404,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a548ff8c0d9357b62dc56ff6057c3daa926c0a1c","tid":953680,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:22:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/保釣行動委員會稱郭紹傑昨起在日本拘留所絕食絕水抗議-023335914.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%A3%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83%E7%A8%B1%E9%83%AD%E7%B4%B9%E5%82%91%E6%98%A8%E8%B5%B7%E5%9C%A8%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%8B%98%E7%95%99%E6%89%80%E7%B5%95%E9%A3%9F%E7%B5%95%E6%B0%B4%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0-023335914.html&d=TQx6GH%2FuAz9pcikEHCQ2%2BNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=32a4f4b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/保釣行動委員會稱郭紹傑昨起在日本拘留所絕食絕水抗議-023335914.html</a><br />\n<br />\n保釣行動委員會成員郭紹傑及嚴敏華，早前在日本靖國神社外抗議後被捕。<br />\n<br />\n保釣行動委員會表示，郭紹傑昨天下午6時開始在拘留所「絕食絕水」抗議，認為日本警察無理拘捕，並在扣押期間受到不合理對待，包括數天不能洗澡。<br />\n<br />\n委員會指，郭紹傑被拘留至今已13天，批評日本政府拖延處理，又在郭紹傑疲勞期間進行訊問。日本律師昨晚到拘留所探望郭紹傑時，得知對方「絕食絕水」，已知會日本警方，並表示會密切留意情況。"},{"pid":"bb3c57a5a1a699b00cb5a961a424a5009f275dce","tid":953680,"uid":41404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:24:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20181224123726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20181224123726&d=TQx6GH%2FuAz9pcikEHCQ2%2BNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=e6af184f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20181224123726</a><br />\n<br />\n香港保釣行動委員會說, 在東京被捕的保釣成員郭紹傑正絕食, 抗議日本政府對他無理拘捕, 以及在拘留中受到不合理待遇.<br />\n        郭紹傑和香港保釣另一名成員嚴敏華, 在今個月12日南京大屠殺81週年前夕, 在東京靖國神社外示威, 要求日本政府承認戰時罪行, 並承擔責任, 期間焚燒日本戰犯東條英機的道具神主牌, 被日本警方拘捕, 扣留至今."},{"pid":"1be8c8713813f935a4da430efc62d8ca1db712c2","tid":953680,"uid":186997,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vd4AfY9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVd4AfY9.png&h=a1c38c3d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8a8a6c3002754bf01ce6e2a742a6bbedc097e03","tid":953680,"uid":9694,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:29:47.000Z","msg":"智障藍屍諗住攪大佢引支那出聲<br />\n佢真係覺得自己好有新聞價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f92ba670e7ee635cb687ac8c69ab12c3b58c7e","tid":953680,"uid":20816,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:38:45.000Z","msg":"插喉啦，條友有自殺傾向"},{"pid":"18049f278800ff9f4dcd136bcff7eb7101cdc40c","tid":953680,"uid":38666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:44:26.000Z","msg":"下年先好返嚟啦<br />\n郭大將軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f7d0fa2e9f81600f4f700ebe6303d4ff1b34a0","tid":953680,"uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:53:11.000Z","msg":"佢由頭到尾都以為好小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"affbbb2f1276a9eb40ed840d1844780a6557709d","tid":953680,"uid":126731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:55:21.000Z","msg":"死係大日本益撚左佢LA."},{"pid":"2e64e1585cb84db8e6bc5c8ad5fa1ba40ac4f34a","tid":953680,"uid":111585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T11:22:18.000Z","msg":"吊死佢啦死仆街"},{"pid":"a0ff5944365fae7172e3cf5c226a083c16c10d83","tid":953680,"uid":130445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T11:25:02.000Z","msg":"睇到呢班傻仔<br />\n好開心"},{"pid":"31c6d05d747105097daebe64a63ebe31a354abf6","tid":953680,"uid":52651,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0